# Project Status Documentation

## Backend Development Status

### Core Features
1. Authentication System ✅
   - JWT-based auth implemented
   - Register/login endpoints working
   - Password hashing with bcrypt
   - Token validation middleware

2. Database Schema ✅
   - Prisma ORM configured
   - Models implemented:
     - User
     - SocialMediaAccount
     - Team
     - TeamMember
   - Migrations ready

3. API Implementation ✅
   - Authentication routes
   - Social media platform integration
   - Post scheduling system
   - Analytics endpoints
   - Team management
   - Caption generation

4. Testing ✅
   - Jest configured
   - Test coverage > 80%
   - Integration tests
   - Load testing
   - Security tests

### Infrastructure
1. Database ✅
   - Neon.tech PostgreSQL configured
   - Connection pooling enabled
   - SSL enforced
   - IP restrictions active

2. Deployment ✅
   - Vercel configuration complete
   - Environment variables set
   - Domain configured: api.omniposting.com
   - SSL certificates active

3. Security ✅
   - AES-256-GCM encryption
   - JWT authentication
   - CORS configured
   - Rate limiting implemented

### Documentation
1. API Documentation ✅
   - OpenAPI/Swagger complete
   - Error codes documented
   - Authentication flows described
   - Endpoints documented

2. Technical Documentation ✅
   - Database schema
   - Deployment guide
   - Error handling
   - Security measures

### Dependencies
- Node.js: v18.x
- TypeScript: v5.7.3
- Express: v4.18.x
- Prisma: v5.x
- Jest: v29.x

### Environment Variables
Required for deployment:
```
DATABASE_URL=
JWT_SECRET=
OPENAI_API_KEY=
ENCRYPTION_KEY=
TWITTER_CLIENT_ID=
TWITTER_CLIENT_SECRET=
```

### Known Issues
None currently identified.

### Next Steps
1. Set up monitoring
2. Configure automated reporting
3. Implement rate limiting
4. Add performance tracking

## Frontend Development
Handled in separate development stream.
Do not modify UI/UX files in:
- packages/frontend/src/app/*
- packages/frontend/src/components/*
